                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Rubrius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Aim</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>aid</abbr><ex>ilis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>praefect</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>soc</abbr><ex>iorum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>in navibus <expan><abbr>long</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Y: 188 v. Chr.: Eingliederung von Fundi in tribus Aemilia; 89 v. Chr.: Amt des praefectus sociorum als terminus ante quem: ab diesem Zeitpunkt nicht mehr in Italien bezeugt.</p>
